              <div align="left"> 
                <p><font size="3" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">Walter Murch 
                  has won three Academy Awards, most recently in 1997, when he 
                  won for picture editing and best sound on "The English Patient." 
                  </font></p>
                <p><font size="3" face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif">In 1980, 
                  he earned an Oscar for best sound and a nomination for picture 
                  cutting on "Apocalypse Now </font></p>
                <p><font size="4"><b><a href="http://www.imdb.com/Bio?Murch,+Walter" target="_blank"><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="3">Mini 
                  biography for Walter Murch</font></a></b></font></p>
                <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="4"><a href="http://us.imdb.com/Name?Murch,+Walter" target="_blank"><b><font size="3">Walter 
                  Murch Filmography</font></b></a><font size="3"><b>&nbsp;&nbsp;</b> 
                  </font></font></p>
                <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif"><b><a href="http://us.imdb.com/name/nm0004555/awards" target="_blank">Awards 
                  for Walter Murch</a></b></font></p>
