                        <font size="2">Director: Walter Murch </font></font></p>
                      <p><font face="Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif" size="2"><i>Considerably 
                        more faithful to the tone of L. Frank Baum's Oz novels, 
                        Return to Oz is exquisitely realized fantasy for smart 
                        youngsters and grownups</i>.. -- <a href="http://hartfordadvocate.com/gbase/Film/content?oid=oid:61211" target="_blank">John 
